#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.24:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga"
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Dutiyasattakasutta"
msgstr "24. Non-Decline for Mendicants (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.24:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that prevent decline."

msgctxt "an7.24:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha … pe …"
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention …"

msgctxt "an7.24:1.3"
msgid "katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that prevent decline?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.24:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū na kammārāmā bhavissanti, na kammaratā, na "
"kammārāmataṃ anuyuttā; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no "
"parihāni."
msgstr ""
"As long as the mendicants don’t relish work, loving it and liking to relish "
"it, they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.24:3.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū na bhassārāmā bhavissanti … pe …"
msgstr "As long as they don’t enjoy talk …"

msgctxt "an7.24:3.2"
msgid "na niddārāmā bhavissanti …"
msgstr "sleep …"

msgctxt "an7.24:3.3"
msgid "na saṅgaṇikārāmā bhavissanti …"
msgstr "company …"

msgctxt "an7.24:3.4"
msgid "na pāpicchā bhavissanti na pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gatā …"
msgstr ""
"they don’t have wicked desires, falling under the sway of wicked desires …"

msgctxt "an7.24:3.5"
msgid "na pāpamittā bhavissanti na pāpasahāyā na pāpasampavaṅkā …"
msgstr "they don’t have bad friends, companions, and associates …"

msgctxt "an7.24:3.6"
msgid ""
"na oramattakena visesādhigamena antarāvosānaṃ āpajjissanti; vuddhiyeva, "
"bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni."
msgstr ""
"they don’t stop half-way after achieving some insignificant distinction, "
"they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.24:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā bhikkhūsu ṭhassanti, "
"imesu ca sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu bhikkhū sandississanti; vuddhiyeva, "
"bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"As long as these seven principles that prevent decline last among the "
"mendicants, and as long as the mendicants are seen following them, they can "
"expect growth, not decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.24:4.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
